## 12. Evaluation Strategy

Full eval strategy per agent (evaluators, CI/CD gate thresholds, LangSmith integration, online eval pipeline) is documented in [PRD Section 7.6](PRD.md#76-ai-evaluation-criteria).

**Quick reference — CI gate thresholds:**

| Eval | Gate Threshold |
|------|---------------|
| Demand decomposition MAPE | < 20% on all eval cases |
| Supply constraint ATP accuracy | Exact match on all eval cases |
| Scenario judge score | ≥ 4.0 overall on all eval cases |
| Financial accuracy | ≤ 15% error on all eval cases |
| Recommendation correctness | Correct or regret < $5,000 on ≥ 80% of eval cases |
| End-to-end generation time (p95) | < 5 minutes |

Any regression on a previously passing eval case blocks the PR merge.

